You can simply ask Alexa to control your device, Such as: light”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Smart Tek APP ” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our Smart Tek app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, IOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search Smart Tek skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable Smart Tek skill, and you'll be navigated to Smart Tek login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on AC.”
“Alexa, turn off AC.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
